Bayes’ rule helps investigators determine the probability that something is true given new evidence.
As the great French mathematician Laplace put it, “The probability of a cause—given an event—is proportional to the probability of the event—given its cause.”


===================

Installing the Python Libraries

python -m pip install --user numpy scipy matplotlib ipython jupyter pandas sympy nose


>>> import numpy

python -m pip install opencv-contrib-python    

or

py -3.7 -m pip install --user opencv-contrib-python

>>> import cv2



